Name: Parliament of Victoria - Legislative Council, Original Papers

About.Hours & facilities: Open Mon-Fri 9am-4:30pm or while Parliament is sitting; closed weekends and public holidays. General reference assistance available.

About.Acquisition focus: Papers, reports, maps, petitions etc tabled in the Victorian Legislative Council.

About.Major holdings: Legislative Council Reports 1856- (100m) Petitions 1856-(50m) Original papers 1856- (300m)
